                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> to <span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span></p><hr /><p>The goblin rabble engage in as coordinated an attack as they can with their dogslicers, attacking each enemy in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:5] (@Check[reflex|dc:18|basic|options:area-effect,inflicts:prone] save). The damage depends on the number of actions. A creature who critically fails their save is also knocked @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Prone].</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> @Damage[1d6[slashing]|options:area-damage] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> @Damage[(2d6+4)[slashing]|options:area-damage] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span> @Damage[(2d6+7)[slashing]|options:area-damage] damage</p>"
