                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The goblin rabble hamstring and hobble as many enemies as possible. Each enemy in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:5] must attempt a @Check[reflex|dc:18] save.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes a –5-foot circumstance penalty to their Speeds.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes a –10-foot circumstance penalty to their Speeds and is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes a –15-foot circumstance penalty to their Speeds and is slowed 1.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.bestiary-effects.Item.Effect: Hobble Pursuit]</p>"
                },
