                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Quickly moving in with grasping hands, the goblin rabble take what they can. The goblin rabble Strides up to twice their Speed. During this movement, the goblins Interact to pick up an unattended object no larger than 2 Bulk or attempt to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Steal] an item from a creature they are adjacent to; the goblins can pick up or Steal as many objects as they have remaining segments in any combination.</p>"
